sense.gloss: main street (as opposed to a side street), high street

meanings: counter for letters, notes, documents, etc.

sdata.j: たくさんの↑人達↑↓ひとたち↓が|↑表通↑↓おもてどお↓り|を↑通↑↓とお↓り↑過↑↓す↓ぎた。
sdata.e: A lot of people went by on the main street.

sdata.j: ↑門↑↓もん↓を↑通↑↓とお↓って|↑表通↑↓おもてどお↓り|に↑出↑↓で↓た。
sdata.e: I went through the gate out onto the street.
